ingredients.ingredient: 1 (16 ounce) package large egg roll wrappers
2 (7 ounce) cans whole fire-roasted mild green chiles
1 ½ cups canola oil for frying

cookingTips: Pat chiles dry to reduce splattering when frying
Keep oil at 350°F for crispy, golden rolls
Fry 2-3 minutes per side until golden brown
enrichment.coachingPrompt: These make great appetizers! Would you like a dipping sauce recommendation?
